The second Friday in January is usually known as Quitter's Day. That's when the majority of people fall off the bandwagon of their well-intentioned New Year's Resolutions.

Well today, quitters win. Take the challenge to quit... toilet paper. Save the planet and you could win just by playing along! Details below: 

Follow our account and tag two friends in the comments to quit toilet paper with you! If you're the lucky winner, all three of you will win a Bio Bidet Slim Edge bidet attachment! 

We will pick a winner Monday, January 17 at noon EST. Good luck, quitters!
